      "body": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Ratopia is a small-scale fancy rat rattery focused on temperament, health and welfare. We keep limited numbers so that every rat is known as an individual."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Our goal is not to chase rare colors, but to build reliable lines you can trust to live in your home and in your hands."
        },
